SNP's software portfolio includes:
CrystalBridge: Visualizes and simulates IT transformation projects
SNP Transformation Backbone with SAP LT: Analyzes and implements changes in SAP systems
SNP Dragoman: Automates the translation process in SAP systems
SNP Data Provisioning & Masking: Supplies and scrambles SAP test data for development systems and QA systems
SNP Interface Scanner: Automatically identifies and documents interfaces in SAP system landscapes
SNP's BLUEFIELDTM approach is a new cloud migration concept that helps companies to reduce the workload and duration required for SAP S/4HANA transformations. The method allows systems to be merged, split, upgraded and harmonized in a single go-live project using automated data and business process tests.
